Brilliant entertainment, amazing tricks and mind ready, all delivered with warm and funny style.
Oct 2024 Couples
We went to see Colin at Harrahs and really enjoyed the experience. The theatre is small enough to be intimate and you feel very engaged with the whole show.
His routine is a mixture of magic and mind reading and he is a master of his craft. How he knows so much so quickly will leave you amazed.
He is slick but warm, and very quick witted. The audience has plenty of chances to take part in the show, and he treats you with respect and tact and makes you feel very comfortable.

The ending is a real head scratcher as to how he does it, and rounded off a great evening.

Worth seeing him now while you can still get tickets
